ygData.messageBody:
Ok, my turn to ask something of you more experienced guys. Out of
curiousity and boredom, I did some exploring and finally found my way to
Cazic Thule. It was a little scary...saw a lot of lizard trains where
everything was yellow to reds. I didn't really go far in...only up to the
first courtyard. Noticed everybody there at the time was between 28-35lvl.
I was the lowest person on the totem pole..being only 21.

Any of you been there yet? Am I way out of my league there? Good tips for
me there for rest spots or areas with Mobs more my league? I heard it's a
good promising area for xp.

I want to kill a lizard! :)
-- Lim'Dul
21 HE Wiz Veeshan
